{"id":569,"date":"2019-05-11T13:49:26","date_gmt":"2019-05-11T11:49:26","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/?p=569"},"modified":"2019-11-23T12:17:09","modified_gmt":"2019-11-23T10:17:09","slug":"oda-cupei-mestruale","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/2019\/05\/11\/oda-cupei-mestruale\/","title":{"rendered":"Od\u0103 cupei menstruale"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Sunt fericita posesoare a dou\u0103 cupe menstruale.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-571\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-300x169.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-768x432.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-680x383.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140143-540x304.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Am auzit de aceast\u0103 minunat\u0103 inven\u021bie \u00eenc\u0103 de acum 8 ani \u00eens\u0103 doar de patru folosesc. Mare p\u0103cat&#8230;este cea mai tare inven\u021bie \u00een igien\u0103 feminin\u0103 pe care eu o cunosc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e2nd am auzit de cup\u0103, acum 8 ani, am fost foarte reticent\u0103. Cum s\u0103 \u00eemi introduc \u00een vagin o a\u0219a bucat\u0103 mare de cauciuc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dup\u0103 patru ani \u0219i documentare am zis &#8222;hai s\u0103 v\u0103d despre ce este vorba&#8221; \u0219i mi-am comandat o cup\u0103 ICare la reducere (35 lei). Pentru mine a fost dragoste la prima utilizare.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Ce este o cup\u0103 menstrual\u0103?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cupa este un &#8222;dispozitiv medical&#8221; din silicon medicinal care introdus\u0103 \u00een vagin \u00een perioada de s\u00e2ngerare menstrual\u0103 colecteaz\u0103 s\u00e2ngele.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cupa se gole\u0219te, \u00een func\u021bie de fluxul personal, cam \u00eentre 2 \u0219i 4 h \u00een primele zile de menstrua\u021bia \u0219i dup\u0103 poate fi \u021binut\u0103 p\u00e2n\u0103 la 12 h. Dup\u0103 golire ea se cl\u0103te\u0219te sub jet de ap\u0103 \u0219i dup\u0103 reintrodus\u0103. La finalul fiec\u0103rei perioade de s\u00e2ngerare menstrual\u0103 cupa se sterilizeaz\u0103 prin fierbere timp de 7-10 minute.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>O cup\u0103 medie\/mare (care este recomandat\u0103 pentru femeile peste 30 de ani \u0219i cele care au copii) are o capacitate de 14 ml. Eu am fost surprins\u0103 s\u0103 observ c\u0103 de\u0219i credeam, c\u00e2nd foloseam absorbante, c\u0103 pierd mult s\u00e2nge nu este a\u0219a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Eu c\u0103l\u0103toresc mult (\u00een general \u00eenafara \u021b\u0103rii) iar cupa este o binecuv\u00e2ntare. M\u0103 simt tot timpul curat\u0103 \u0219i uscat\u0103 (ca \u00een reclam\u0103). Atunci c\u00e2nd golesc cupa \u00eentr-o toalet\u0103 f\u0103r\u0103 ap\u0103 curent\u0103 \u00een interior, o cl\u0103tesc cu ap\u0103 dintr-o sticl\u0103 sau pur \u0219i simplu \u00eei \u0219terg cercul de sus cu pu\u021bin\u0103 h\u00e2rtie \u0219i o reintroduc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Avantajele cupei menstruale (pentru mine)<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Control asupra cantit\u0103\u021bii de s\u00e2nge menstrual<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0218tiu exact c\u00e2t s\u00e2nge menstrual am pierdut \u00een fiecare lun\u0103 \u0219i pot observa dac\u0103 apar deregl\u0103ri, schimb\u0103ri radicale.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Protec\u021bie p\u00e2n\u0103 la 12 ore<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>O cup\u0103 poate fi \u021binut\u0103 \u00eentre 2 \u0219i 12 ore, \u00een func\u021bie de fluxul fiec\u0103rei femei. Recunosc \u00eens\u0103 c\u0103 uneori am uitat de ea, da am uitat c\u0103 o am, \u0219i am \u021binut-o  \u0219i mai mult.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Este prietenoas\u0103 cu mediul<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prin utilizarea cupei mediul este protejat. Durata de descompunere a absorbantelor este una foarte mare. A\u0219adar prin utilizarea cupei evit\u0103m poluarea produs\u0103 at\u00e2t pentru producerea absorbantelor c\u00e2t \u0219i cu acestea dup\u0103 utilizare.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>U\u0219or de introdus \u0219i scos fiind din cauciuc medicinal<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cupa este din cauciuc medicinal (nu con\u021bine latex) astfel se pliaz\u0103 foarte u\u0219or \u0219i se poate introduce.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Eu am dou\u0103 tipuri: ICare \u0219i Viva Cup. Cea ICare este mai rigid\u0103 \u0219i, din punctul meu de vedere, mai u\u0219or de introdus (manipulat), se desface singur\u0103 mai u\u0219or \u0219i face vid. Viva Cup este din material mai moale \u0219i astfel se desface pu\u021bin mai greu \u00een interior. Dar consider c\u0103 este o chestiune de gusturi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-570\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-300x169.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-768x432.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-680x383.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/IMG_20190511_140102-540x304.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Reutilizabil\u0103<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cupa poate fi folosit\u0103 p\u00e2n\u0103 la 10 ani. Astfel economisind bani \u0219i protej\u00e2nd totodat\u0103 mediul.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dup\u0103 fiecare ciclu menstrual ea trebuie sterilizat\u0103 prin fierbere. Dup\u0103 fiecare golire poate fi sp\u0103lat\u0103 sub jet de ap\u0103 \u0219i refolosit\u0103.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>De c\u00e2nd folosesc cupa, \u0219i am v\u0103zut c\u0103 este &#8222;cea mai tare inven\u021bie dup\u0103 roat\u0103&#8221;, povestesc despre ea tuturor prietenelor. Sunt foarte \u00eenc\u00e2ntat\u0103 \u0219i o recomand.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><div><br><\/div><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sunt fericita posesoare a dou\u0103 cupe menstruale. Am auzit de aceast\u0103 minunat\u0103 inven\u021bie \u00eenc\u0103 de acum 8 ani \u00eens\u0103 doar de patru folosesc. Mare p\u0103cat&#8230;este cea mai tare inven\u021bie \u00een&nbsp;[&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":571,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7,5,1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/569"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=569"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/569\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":574,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/569\/revisions\/574"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/571"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=569"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddab